{"tid":1712580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非既你地都有野做 高調宣傳警察係暴大敗退！！","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T23:28:59.000Z","uid":111425,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"762a4ae41d2eb6fc2bbd5b22099482c522af5c80","tid":1712580,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:47:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">知唔知今次暴大手足做左咩<br />\n就係半年來第一次打陣地戰係贏左啊<br />\n我地要高調咁宣傳今次班狗係暴大打左兩日出埋水炮車都係敗退<br />\n幫手令班狗<br />\n同只睇tvb 既藍絲對佢地覺得係敵既仆街終於輸第一次<br />\n好重要嫁！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e350faddbf2caa02a22ae56d4714929b737bfe0b","tid":1712580,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"df171555e2100394deeef00fef70f73e512c823e","tid":1712580,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"我想講一講既係防暴分區唔係用18區<br />\n而係港島、東九、西九、新界南、新界北<br />\n<br />\n暴大所在既沙田, 屬於新界南<br />\n如果想用區開花去救佢的話<br />\n可以吹雞 荃+葵+青+東涌+沙+馬+火炭呢啲集中開花<br />\n拉對角線最長距離去打<br />\n<br />\n其他區保持有零散開花去迫佢留住兵力<br />\n<br />\n而家集中晒沙田大埔<br />\n沙田屬新界南<br />\n大埔屬新界北<br />\n只會被兩區輕取....<br />\n就算十八區開花要開得有智慧<br />\n//<a href=\"https://t.me/hknimC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhknimC%2F&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7bhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=06bb3d97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknimC/</a>"},{"pid":"a70cbbb77ac452a2e89d23c0a0f0598d401425c8","tid":1712580,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab8fb8216778dd1b1822b837acfc94dbf9bcbf9d","tid":1712580,"uid":136700,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"慘勝"},{"pid":"f405ff4fb4a650a77fa9a06f8e1c49a54ab73dec","tid":1712580,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91c5185bfcdc8d7657a3357b45